---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="FlightGear Polska - Techniczne Centrum Operacyjne" description="Darmowy symulator lotu. Pobierz FlightGear Nightly. Boeing 737 JSBSim, polska sceneria VFR, brutalna fizyka lotu bez arcade.">
  
  <header class="fixed w-full top-0 z-50 bg-black/95 backdrop-blur-md border-b-2 border-cyan-900/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <div class="h-10 flex items-center gap-4">
        <img src="/assets/logo.png" alt="FlightGear Polska Logo" class="h-full object-contain" />
        <span class="text-xl font-black tracking-widest text-white uppercase hidden sm:block">FLIGHTGEAR <span class="text-cyan-500">POLSKA</span></span>
      </div>
      <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-bold text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-widest">
        <a href="https://github.com/flightgear-polska" target="_blank" title="Składnica Kodu GitHub FlightGear Polska" class="hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">GitHub [CODE]</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/" target="_blank" title="Społeczność Discord FGPL" class="hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Discord [COMMS]</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="bg-black text-white selection:bg-cyan-500 selection:text-black">
    
    <!-- BRUTALIST HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 border-b-2 border-cyan-900/50 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-gray-900">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/85 z-10"></div>
        <div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-cyan-900/30 text-xs font-mono border-4 border-dashed border-cyan-900/20 m-2">
           <span>[ RAW VIDEO LOOP ]</span>
           <span>TURBINE START / LOW PASS MVT</span>
           <span>NO AUDIO / WEBM H.265</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-20">
        <div class="max-w-5xl pt-10">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none mb-6 text-white drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.3)]">
            FLIGHTGEAR POLSKA <br/>
            <span class="text-cyan-500">– OFICJALNE CENTRUM OPERACYJNE.</span>
          </h1>
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-10 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-6 leading-relaxed">
            FIZYKA MÓWI SAMA ZA SIEBIE. <br/>
            <span class="text-cyan-400">SPOŁECZNOŚĆ PONAD KORPORACJĘ.</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 mb-12">
            <a href="https://www.flightgear.org/download/" target="_blank" class="px-8 py-5 bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-500 text-black font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm transition-all text-center drop-shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)]">
              [ POBIERZ FLIGHTGEAR Z KANAŁU STABLE ]
            </a>
            <a href="https://download.flightgear.org/builds/nightly/" target="_blank" class="px-8 py-5 bg-transparent border-2 border-cyan-600 hover:border-cyan-400 hover:bg-cyan-900/20 text-cyan-500 font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm transition-all text-center">
              [ POBIERZ NIGHTLY 2024.X (Wymagane do nowej grafiki HDR) ]
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- PRE-FLIGHT CHECK / MASTER FOLDER BUG FLAG -->
          <div class="bg-red-900/20 border border-red-500/50 p-6 rounded-sm max-w-3xl">
             <h3 class="text-red-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 border-b border-red-500/30 pb-2 inline-block">:: PRE-FLIGHT CHECK (Krytyczne Zabezpieczenie)</h3>
             <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
               Instalujesz samolot pobrany z GitHuba jako ZIP? <strong class="text-white">Bezwzględnie usuń przyrostek <code>-master</code> lub <code>-main</code> z nazwy folderu przed wrzuceniem go do Aircrafts.</strong> W przeciwnym razie silnik pominie instrukcje XML, a systemy FDM i awionika ulegną awarii.
             </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LIVE OPERATIONS WIDGET -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-black border-b border-cyan-900/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
         <div class="mb-12">
           <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter border-b-4 border-cyan-500 pb-2 inline-block mb-4">:: Ruch Nad Polską (Live Map Protocol)</h2>
           <br/>
           <span class="text-black bg-cyan-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-1 text-sm rounded-sm">NIE LEĆ SAM. DOŁĄCZ DO RUCHU NAD POLSKĄ.</span>
         </div>

         <div class="border border-cyan-900/50 bg-gray-900 rounded-sm overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto">
           <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse font-mono text-sm min-w-max">
             <thead>
               <tr class="bg-black border-b border-cyan-900/50 text-cyan-500">
                 <th class="p-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Callsign</th>
                 <th class="p-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Aircraft</th>
                 <th class="p-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Altitude</th>
                 <th class="p-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Heading</th>
               </tr>
             </thead>
             <tbody class="text-gray-300">
               <!-- PLACEHOLDERS FOR MP-MAP WIDGET -->
               <tr class="border-b border-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition">
                 <td class="p-4 font-bold text-white">SP-NTX</td>
                 <td class="p-4">Boeing 737-800YV</td>
                 <td class="p-4">34000 ft</td>
                 <td class="p-4">270&deg;</td>
               </tr>
               <tr class="border-b border-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition">
                 <td class="p-4 font-bold text-white">PLF-101</td>
                 <td class="p-4">Gulfstream G550</td>
                 <td class="p-4">12000 ft</td>
                 <td class="p-4">090&deg;</td>
               </tr>
               <tr class="border-b border-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition">
                 <td class="p-4 font-bold text-white">VAF-22</td>
                 <td class="p-4">F-16C Block 52+</td>
                 <td class="p-4">4000 ft</td>
                 <td class="p-4">350&deg;</td>
               </tr>
               <tr class="text-center">
                 <td colspan="4" class="p-4 bg-black/50 text-cyan-900 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs italic">[ Dane oczekują na skrypt WebSocket Fetch z mpmap02.flightgear.org ]</td>
               </tr>
             </tbody>
           </table>
         </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- JSBSIM ELITE CATALOG -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-black container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter border-b-4 border-cyan-500 pb-2 inline-block mb-6">:: Elitarna Flota Maszyn</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-10 border-l-4 border-gray-600 pl-4 max-w-4xl leading-relaxed">
          Zostawiliśmy arkadową fizykę za drzwiami. ZERO tolerancji dla uproszczeń. Tylko brutalny, nieliniowy i matematyczny model lotu sprawdzony w wirtualnych tunelach wiatrowych JSBSim.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <article class="border-2 border-cyan-900/30 bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-sm hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors group flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -right-12 top-4 bg-cyan-900/70 text-cyan-400 text-[10px] font-black px-12 py-1 rotate-45 uppercase tracking-widest border-y border-cyan-500/50">JSBSim Certified</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors mt-2">Boeing 737-800YV</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">FDM: JSBSim<br/>Systems: Study-Level<br/>License: GPL</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/flightgear-polska" target="_blank" class="block w-full text-center py-3 bg-black hover:bg-cyan-900 text-cyan-500 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest border border-cyan-900/50 transition-colors">[ REPOZYTORIUM ]</a>
          </article>
          
          <article class="border-2 border-cyan-900/30 bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-sm hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors group flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -right-12 top-4 bg-cyan-900/70 text-cyan-400 text-[10px] font-black px-12 py-1 rotate-45 uppercase tracking-widest border-y border-cyan-500/50">JSBSim Certified</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors mt-2">Cessna 172P</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">FDM: JSBSim<br/>Systems: Full C&D / Interactive<br/>License: GPL</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://wiki.flightgear.org/Cessna_172P" target="_blank" class="block w-full text-center py-3 bg-black hover:bg-cyan-900 text-cyan-500 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest border border-cyan-900/50 transition-colors">[ DOKUMENTACJA WIKI ]</a>
          </article>

          <article class="border-2 border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-sm hover:border-white/50 transition-colors group flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-400 mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-white transition-colors mt-2">MiG-21 Bis</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-500 mb-6 leading-relaxed">FDM: YASim<br/>Systems: Combat/Radar Simulation<br/>License: GPL</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/flightgear-polska" target="_blank" class="block w-full text-center py-3 bg-black hover:bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest border border-gray-800 transition-colors">[ REPOZYTORIUM ]</a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FGPL DEV STUDIO PRIDE BANNER -->
      <div class="mb-24">
         <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-900/10 via-cyan-900/30 to-black border-2 border-cyan-500/50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)] relative overflow-hidden">
            
            <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 w-64 h-64 bg-cyan-600/10 blur-[60px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

            <div class="max-w-2xl relative z-10">
               <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">FGPL DEV STUDIO FLAGSHIP</h3>
               <h4 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase text-white mb-6">PZL Koliber 150 <span class="bg-cyan-600 text-black px-3 py-1 text-2xl">WIP</span></h4>
               <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 font-mono leading-relaxed mb-8">
                 Projekt dumy narodowej środowiska symulacyjnego FlightGear. Tworzymy najwierniejszą publicznie dostępną kopię PZL Koliber w oparciu o autorskie modelce lotu C++. 
                 <strong class="text-white bg-black/50 px-2 py-1 block mt-2 border-l-2 border-cyan-500 text-sm">Potrafisz modelować w Blenderze? Piszesz w Nasal API? Posiadasz licencję PPL(A)?</strong>
               </p>
               <p class="text-2xl font-black uppercase text-cyan-400 tracking-tighter">POMÓŻ NAM ULEPSZYĆ POLSKIE NIEBO.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10 w-full lg:w-auto">
               <a href="https://github.com/flightgear-polska" target="_blank" class="block w-full text-center px-10 py-6 bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-500 text-black font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm transition-all drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.5)] whitespace-nowrap">
                 [ DOŁĄCZ DO DEWELOPERÓW ]
               </a>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-900 border-t border-cyan-900/50 py-12 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
         <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">FGPL Operations Center /// EST. 2020-2026</p>
         <p class="text-cyan-900 text-xs font-mono font-black uppercase tracking-widest">FIZYKA PONAD GRAFIKĘ. SPOŁECZNOŚĆ PONAD KORPORACJĘ.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/flightgearpolska" title="32k views social proof" target="_blank" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-500 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest transition-colors">YouTube [32K+]</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/flightgear-polska" target="_blank" title="Oficjalne Repozytorium GitHub" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-500 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest transition-colors">GitHub [CODE]</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
